<div id="faq-overlay" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.65);z-index:500;align-items:center;justify-content:center;backdrop-filter:blur(5px)">
  <div class="modal" style="max-height:80vh;overflow-y:auto;max-width:460px">
    <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <div style="margin-top:4px">
      <div style="padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#002147;margin-bottom:4px">How do I change my PIN?</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#475569">Go to Menu → Change passcode, enter your current PIN and then your new 4-digit PIN twice to confirm.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#002147;margin-bottom:4px">When will my debit card arrive?</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#475569">Your card is currently in transit. A FidBank UK representative will hand-deliver it to your registered address in a sealed envelope. Typically within 3-5 business days of dispatch.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#002147;margin-bottom:4px">Is my money protected?</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#475569">Yes. FidBank UK Limited is FSCS protected. Your eligible deposits are protected up to £120,000 per person.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#002147;margin-bottom:4px">How do I report fraud?</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#475569">Contact us immediately via Secure Messages or call our 24/7 fraud hotline. Never share your PIN or password with anyone, including FidBank staff.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:12px 0">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#002147;margin-bottom:4px">How do I open a savings account?</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#475569">Go to Menu → Apply for new product, select Savings Account and follow the on-screen instructions. It takes less than 5 minutes.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="m-acts" style="margin-top:16px">
      <button class="btn-p" onclick="closeFAQ()">Close</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

